<div class="container">

    <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse1">Who are you?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    My name is Dan, I'm a Registered Dietitian by day and a passionate programmer by night.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2">What is this place?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    This site's goal is to streamline some of the calculations that need to be done by clinical dietitians many times throughout their standard day.
                    As important as it is to understand the equations and calculations, having to do them by hand on large volume of patients can become tedious which can introduce human error.
                    Human error can still come into play here when it comes to number entry, but it can help minimize this while saving a vast amount of time throughout the day.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse3">I have a comment/suggestion/issue!</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    If you have any questions, concerns, or suggestions please feel free to <a href="mailto:synergy.harm@gmail.com">email</a> or tweet me <a href="https://twitter.com/Cinder0us">@@Cinder0us</a>!
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse4">How can I help?</a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    I do this in my spare time as part of a sideproject but it costs money to keep the site up and running! Any tips/donations would be greatly appreciated and 100% of it would go straight towards maintaining this site!
